title: SPECTACULAR VIEWS IN QUANTUM ON THE BAY!
posting_body: ['Experience spectacular water views from this corner residence in Quantum on the Bay.', 'Enjoy beautiful sunrises over the Bay & Ocean (direct East) from a large balcony in the living room or from a wraparound terrace off the primary bedroom.', 'The condo features floor-to-ceiling hurricane impact windows, porcelain tile floor throughout.', 'Ample closet space - a walk-in closet in the master and 2 separate closets in the second bedroom.', 'Each bedroom has its own ensuite bathroom, plus a powder room at the main space.', 'Quantum on the Bay is centrally located in Edgewater, directly across from the park, and offers resort-style amenities that include a multi-level fitness center, two swimming pools, a 24-hour lobby attendant, and valet parking.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
